                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6331" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1613</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9164 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信多元化战略：盲人瞎马还是运筹帷幄</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is Hisense&#39;s diversification blind or strategic</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐文秀，舒永有，唐悦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信集团；多元化战略；战略发展；核心竞争力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense Group; Diversification strategy；Strategic development; Core Competence</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着人口红利的消失和国内家电行业产业链的成熟健全，品牌格局趋稳，行业竞争激烈，海信集团和众多家电企业一样面临着市场僧多粥少的困局。多元化跨河过界成了不少家电企业抵经营风险的出路。历经50余载的发展，海信的业务几乎覆盖了全部家电领域，同时还涉足了电子产品、IT、智能信息系统、现代服务等领域。在5G新零售当道，AI加持的互联网+共享时代下消费者消费行为的改变也是海信集团开辟更多新业态、新领域，去满足不同体验消费的需求的多元化机遇。本案例主要梳理海信集团从彩电领军品牌的优势基础上有远见地一步步从家电、智能信息系统、现代服务业到高科技板块，甚至在新能源汽车等多个领域进军的多元化历程，旨在探讨海信多元化布局的动因和实现路径，对分析多元化布局的风险和实施该战略所需具备的条件提供一定的启示。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the disappearance of demographic dividend and the mature and sound industrial chain of domestic home appliance industry, the brand pattern is stabilizing and the industry competition is fierce. Hisense Group, like many home appliance enterprises, is facing the dilemma of more than enough people to work out the market. Diversification across rivers and borders has become the way out for many home appliance enterprises to offset business risks. In the era of 5G new retail and Internet + sharing supported by AI, the change of consumer consumption behavior is also a diversified opportunity for Hisense Group to open up more new business forms and fields to meet the needs of different experience consumption. This case mainly summarizes the diversified process of Hisense Group in multi-media, home appliances, IT intelligent information system, modern service industry, even new energy vehicles and other fields on the basis of its advantages as a leading brand of color TV, aiming to explore the motivation and realization path of Hisense&#39;s diversified layout. It provides some enlightenment to analyze the risk of diversified layout and the conditions needed for the implementation of the strategy.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">多元化战略分类、多元化的程度、核心竞争力；战略环境(SWOT分析)；多元化战略动因、多元化战略风险；核心竞争力、价值链理论、战略评价标准；多元化协同效应、核心竞争力、动态能力理论、头部战略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-06</td>
                            </tr>
